[{"type":"heading","level":2,"children":[{"text":"Session Summary"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Project: YouTube Playlist Analytics | Date: 2026-03-25 | Messages: 1001"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"children":[{"text":"Conversation Excerpt"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🧑 You"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"# MISSION DIRECTIVE: AUTONOMOUS APP GENERATION with ADVANCED CAPABILITIES\n**Role:** You are an autonomous Expert Full-Stack AI Engineer with advanced multi-modal capabilities.\n**Objective:** You will build a complete, highly advanced clone of the SaaS platform [Sandcastles.ai](https://www.sandcastles.ai/) entirely from scratch, operating completely autonomously. This clone will not only replicate the core features but also integrate significantly improved capabilities.\n**Rules of Engagement:** 1. The user DOES NOT want to use the terminal manually. You are authorized to execute all necessary terminal commands to scaffold the app, install dependencies, and configure the environment.\n2. Do not ask for permission for every single file creation or minor command. Outline your immediate plan, ex"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🤖 Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Directive acknowledged. Here's my understanding:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"**What I'm building:** A dark-mode SaaS platform for content creators — viral video research, multi-modal AI script generation, vault of hooks/styles, and creator channel tracking. Core stack: Next.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind, Shadcn UI, Supabase, OpenAI, Stripe."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"**Key differentiator:** GPT-4o Vision pipeline analyzing video screenshots to extract visual editing tactics (\"Vision\" feature)."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🤖 Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"The project doesn't exist yet — I'll create it non-interactively and then build all the architecture."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🤖 Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Next.js 14 project created. Now installing all core dependencies in parallel."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🤖 Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"All dependencies installed. Now building the entire architecture — all files simultaneously."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`\n- Zustand uses a \"slice\" pattern where you define state + actions together in `create()`. For a complex app like this, we keep everything in one store but organize by domain (nav, modal, user prefs).\n- Next.js Server Actions (`\"use server\"`) run entirely on the server — OpenAI API keys never reach the browser. The function is called like a regular async function from client components.\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Let me now build all the files. I'll do this in parallel batches:"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"children":[{"text":"🤖 Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Now the AI Server Actions:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"... and 995 more messages in this session."}]}]
